1. --> Authentication and authorization ke liye humein sabse pehle kuch cheezein seekhni hai, see below:-
    a) Cookies kaise set karte hain
    b) Bcrypt kaise  use karte hain for password encryption and deecryption
    c) jwt kya hai and jwt mein data kaise store kare or bahar kaise nikale

2. --> install this package first--> npm i jsonwebtoken bcrypt
